inc.solutions.numerical

Interface Matrix_Solve_Behavior

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Gaussian_Solver_Behavior, Matrix_Inversion_Behavior, NullBehavior

    public interface Matrix_Solve_Behavior
    This is an interface that contain only ona method to declare the matrix solving behavior of each possible mathematical method. After implementing this method, any subclass can be used in the LinearSolverDeluxe system.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Muaz Kurt
